name: Christmas Card- Xmas Tree (10 pc)
description:
These imported cards will pop up into a 3D christmas tree that hang in a snowball shape frame. The stars and ornaments on the tree are metallic red and there are glitters on the edge of the tree.

It is a piece of paper art. 

It will be a pack of 10 pieces. 

Size: 5.125" x 4.75" x 3"

name: Christmas Card- Sleigh (10 pc)
description:
These imported cards stand as rocking sleigh. It has 3 layers of cute illustration of dog, kids, and christmas tree.
The sleigh is bronze metallic color. There are some glitters that adds the winter/season accent.
You can write notes/messages on the back of the card.
 
It is a pack of 10 pieces.

Size: 3.75" x 3" x 1"
